name: 3D Frog Feast Free
description:
The frog is hungry. Really hungry. Help the frog gobble up all the food in super cool looking 3D mazes!

Watch out for natural frog enemies such as snakes! While the frog is eating the food, the snakes try to eat the frog. Only when the frog eats a special power vitamin can he turn the tables on the snakes. Clear all the mazes to become top frog champion and earn your place among your peers.

This game is filled with super fun retro arcade action and hilarious fun!

This FREE version of 3D Frog Feast contains 5 complete levels.

Features:

* 5 amazing mazes
* High-scores table
* Super addicting game-play
* Retro arcade action
* Cool soundtrack
* Super cool frog

Compatibility:

* iPhone
* iPod Touch
* iPad
